    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors have been assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed the required credibility level for a Medium model risk, Medium model influence, Medium decision consequence context of use. The single below-requirement factor (Test conditions, achieved 1 vs. required 2) is accepted on the basis that ASTM F1717 prescribes a single standardised test condition, regulatory precedent supports single-condition testing for this device class, and the remaining twelve factors provide sufficient compensating evidence. All three primary QoIs satisfy the pre-specified acceptance bounds (<10% percentage difference, E/uval < 1.96). The FEA modeling framework is assessed as credible for the stated COU.",
